      "summary": "提供字段组件初始化属性解析工具，根据字段配置中的 component 名称从注入系统查找对应的 InjectionKey 并 inject 获取默认属性。",
      "tags": ["utility", "field", "injection", "form"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/vant-pro/src/components/form/constants/index.ts",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "index.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/vant-pro/src/components/form/constants/index.ts",
      "summary": "定义表单组件映射表(BaseComponentMap)和组件名称联合类型(ComponentName)，将 Vant UI 组件(field、picker、switch 等)映射为运行时可用组件，并支持通过 TypeScript 声明合并扩展自定义组件。",
      "tags": ["constants", "component-map", "type-definition", "form", "barrel"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 TypeScript 声明合并(declaration merging)扩展 ComponentMap 接口，允许外部模块添加自定义组件映射。"
    },
    {
