      "name": "useFields.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/vant-pro/src/components/form/hooks/useFields.ts",
      "summary": "类型安全的 useFields Hook 封装，将 core 层的泛型参数绑定为 Vant Pro 本地类型(Field<ComponentName, D> 和 FieldInstance)，确保字段配置的类型推导正确。",
      "tags": ["hook", "form", "re-export", "type-definition"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/vant-pro/src/components/form/hooks/useForm.ts",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "useForm.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/vant-pro/src/components/form/hooks/useForm.ts",
      "summary": "Vant Pro 核心表单 Hook，基于 core useForm 封装并额外集成 formPopup(弹出层表单管理)，支持函数重载以兼容不同的初始化参数签名。",
      "tags": ["hook", "form", "popup", "entry-point", "composable"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "使用 TypeScript 函数重载(overload signatures)支持两种调用方式：(formData, fields, root) 和 (root)。"
    },
    {
      "id": "file:packages/vant-pro/src/components/form/hooks/useFormPopup.ts",
      "type": "file",
      "name": "useFormPopup.ts",
      "filePath": "packages/vant-pro/src/components/form/hooks/useFormPopup.ts",
      "summary": "管理 Vant 移动端表单弹出层(Popup)的 Hook，使用 provide/inject 模式实现父子表单间的弹出层状态共享，支持打开/关闭指定路径字段的弹出层并动态更新 Popup 属性。",
      "tags": ["hook", "popup", "form", "provide-inject", "mobile"],
      "complexity": "moderate",
      "languageNotes": "通过 provide/inject 模式实现弹出层状态在组件树中的共享，非根组件通过 inject 获取父级 store 避免重复创建。"
    },
