      "summary": "类型安全的 useFormRef Hook 封装，将 core 层的泛型参数绑定为 Vant 的 FormInstance 类型，用于获取表单组件实例引用。",
      "tags": ["hook", "form", "re-export", "type-definition"],
      "complexity": "simple"
    },
    {
